<plot>The fascinating story of Luca Prodan, Italo-Scottish Idol of Argentina's mythical 'SUMO' Rock Band, and innovator of Latin American rock. His past as a pupil in Gordonstoun, Scotland's elitist college. His rebellious adolescence and fatal flirtation with heroin. His London years in the heart of the Punk explosion, and miraculous 're-birth' in dictatorship-ridden Argentina. South America's Ian Curtis... with a twist.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?346289</url></doc>
